To solve larger problem, use mumps or percodintioner which would work with saddle problems. Otherwaise you will have problems.

./transport -my_file ../atom_tests/simple_thermal_problem.h5m \
-ksp_type fgmres \
-pc_type lu -pc_factor_mat_solver_package mumps -ksp_monitor \
-my_order 4 \
-my_max_post_proc_ref_level 3
